{"tid":950644,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"後生港女賣自己朋友","createTime":"2018-12-21T16:43:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T23:12:34.000Z","uid":125075,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"44d1e5449c3416ede041ab4af210e3271f424f62","tid":950644,"uid":125075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:43:43.000Z","msg":"我朋友因為信左佢既同學去見一份批發工 事前一啲詳情都唔透露 話佢做開無問題幾好做 咁我朋友就搵緊工 咁信左朋友就上左去 個下先發現係聽洗腦講座 2pm-11pm一直洗腦式唔比走 仲叫佢比錢 咁我朋友無帶錢係身 就比佢地帶左落樓下禁錢先比走 比完錢就話留記錄要佢拎身分證明影印 最後先走得到<br />\n可能各位巴絲會覺得我朋友唔知世途險惡 咁蠢比人呃左上去 但事後佢已經即刻打算解決追究 都知道拎唔番啲錢 但真係好唔憤氣想將個賤人貼出黎等大家認住佢 唔好比佢搵到食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e84c52fad8e3513f47379177113a461ef15a2fad","tid":950644,"uid":212317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:47:12.000Z","msg":"報驚啦屌  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65e8e028af263be3fb1dd49e97eda2dc7a3234b","tid":950644,"uid":125075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e84c52fad8e3513f47379177113a461ef15a2fad","tid":950644,"uid":212317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:47:12.000Z","msg":"報驚啦屌  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:48:45.000Z","msg":"上網睇過好多受害者報左都無用 佢又一啲證據都無 單同收據咩都無 得wts記錄"},{"pid":"d14868daa0e8fb4c6495a7646a5ca9f829e3a1c7","tid":950644,"uid":212317,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"咁幾千銀當買教訓 + 唱哀佢<br />\n<br />\n都無計  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw 呃錢狗死全家"},{"pid":"dc17a9b4debb0093bdf4f299248721b26288bcee","tid":950644,"uid":12143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:59:40.000Z","msg":"慘 點解唔報警當時"},{"pid":"aba210c94ddc345271e0da060cd91f08e5835b9e","tid":950644,"uid":205134,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score